<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Skill Sharing Platform</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family:sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        header {
            background: #007BFF;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 35px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
        .logo-img {
            width: 60px; 
            height: 60px; 
        }
        .auth-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .auth-link {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #28a745;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .auth-link:hover {
            background: #218838;
        }
        .main-content {
            margin-left: 220px;
            padding: 20px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .quote {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .quote img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-content">
            <img src="https://tse2.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.9xYSorMRnQt8z7b71ocUTAHaHa&pid=Api&P=0&h=180" alt="Logo" class="logo-img">
            <div class="logo">Skill Sharing Platform</div>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-links">
            <a href="/signin" class="auth-link">Signin</a>
            <a href="/signup" class="auth-link">Signup</a>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="quote">
            <p>"Sharing knowledge is the most fundamental act of friendship. Because it is a way you can give something without losing something." - Richard Stallman</p>
            <img src="https://www.skillshare.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/skillshare-badges.jpg" alt="Inspiring Image">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
